query:
SELECT pg_advisory_xact_lock(hashtext(concat(
            currency,
            journal_id::text,
            account_id::text,
            velocity_control_id::text,
            velocity_limit_id::text
        )))
        FROM UNNEST(
            $1::text[], 
            $2::uuid[], 
            $3::uuid[], 
            $4::uuid[], 
            $5::uuid[]
        )
        AS v(currency, journal_id, account_id, velocity_control_id, velocity_limit_id)
